data.description: FEATURING ONE OF OUR MODERN FARMHOUSE PLANS ON ONE ACRE.  BEAUTIFUL BACKYARD THAT BACKS UP TO WOODED AREA.  OPEN CONCEPT 4 BEDROOM, 3 FULL BATHS, 2 CAR GARAGE WITH EXTRA STORAGE AREA.  KITCHEN AND DINING ARE OPEN TO THE LIVING AREA.  GREAT FOR ENTERTAINING!  4TH BEDROOM CAN ALSO BE USED AS A STUDY.  FLEX-PLAYROOM OFF OF THE SECONDARY BEDROOMS.  MASTER SUITE BOASTS SEPARATE VANITIES WITH A NICE SIZED WALK IN SHOWER AND HUGE WALK IN CLOSET.  UTILITY IS LOCATED OFF OF THE MASTER CLOSET FOR CONVENIENCE.
